# PMDD System Architecture Figures

*Note for Researchers: These Mermaid diagrams are formatted for direct inclusion in academic publications. They can be natively rendered in GitHub or exported to SVG/PDF via any standard Markdown editor.*

## Figure 1: Full Multi-Agent Pipeline

```mermaid
graph TD
    classDef LLM fill:#0f172a,stroke:#64ffda,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef Deterministic fill:#1e293b,stroke:#f87171,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef Data fill:#334155,stroke:#94a3b8,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff;

    A[Raw Corpus Input]:::Data --> B[Agent 1: Preprocessor]:::LLM
    B --> C[Agent 0: Profiler]:::LLM
    
    C -->|Proposes Execution Plan| D{Deterministic Governance Layer}:::Deterministic
    
    D -->|Enforced Routing| E[Agent 2: Pragmatics]:::LLM
    D -->|Enforced Routing| F[Agent 3: Semantics]:::LLM
    D -->|Enforced Routing| G[Agent 4: Register]:::LLM
    
    E & F & G --> H[Agent 5: Orchestrator]:::LLM
    
    H --> I[Mathematical Engine]:::Deterministic
    I --> J[Final Export: JSON/CSV/MD]:::Data
```

## Figure 2: Deterministic Governance Workflow

```mermaid
graph TD
    classDef Logic fill:#1e293b,stroke:#64ffda,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef Decision fill:#0f172a,stroke:#f87171,stroke-width:2px,shape:diamond,color:#fff;
    classDef Output fill:#334155,stroke:#94a3b8,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff;

    A[Profiler Plan Received]:::Logic --> B{Is Domain Overridden?}:::Decision
    B -->|Yes| C[Force Framework Activation]:::Logic
    B -->|No| D[Accept Profiler Frameworks]:::Logic
    
    C & D --> E[Agents Execute Analysis]:::Logic
    E --> F[Raw Confidences Generated]:::Logic
    
    F --> G{Is Emotional Complexity > 0.8?}:::Decision
    G -->|Yes| H[Multiply Confidence by 0.85]:::Logic
    G -->|No| I[Retain Base Confidence]:::Logic
    
    F --> J{Is Evidence Quality < 0.5?}:::Decision
    J -->|Yes| K[Multiply Confidence by 0.70]:::Logic
    J -->|No| L[Retain Base Confidence]:::Logic
    
    H & I & K & L --> M[Log to Traceability Audit]:::Output
```

## Figure 3: Systemic Uncertainty Propagation

```mermaid
graph LR
    classDef Base fill:#0f172a,stroke:#64ffda,color:#fff;
    classDef Penalty fill:#1e293b,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff;
    classDef Final fill:#334155,stroke:#94a3b8,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;

    A[Pragmatics: 0.90]:::Base --> D[Governance Filter]:::Penalty
    B[Semantics: 0.82]:::Base --> D
    C[Register: 0.88]:::Base --> D
    
    D -->|Penalty Applied| E[Pragmatics: 0.90]:::Base
    D -->|Complexity Slash| F[Semantics: 0.69]:::Penalty
    D -->|Penalty Applied| G[Register: 0.88]:::Base
    
    E & F & G --> H[Average: 0.823]:::Final
    H --> I[Systemic Uncertainty Index: 0.177]:::Final
```
